00:47:00,769 --> 00:47:01,869
Kenapa Anda tertawa?

525
00:47:03,700 --> 00:47:05,669
Ambil lagi bonekanya dan temui dia.

526
00:47:06,800 --> 00:47:08,639
Anda tahu apa soal kami sampai bisa berkata begitu?

527
00:47:10,110 --> 00:47:12,240
Konon, kita sulit memberi nasihat atas masalah sendiri,

528
00:47:13,110 --> 00:47:16,209
